  "sections" : [ {
    "type" : "verse",
    "label" : "VERSE 1",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "God forgave my sin in Jesus' name,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 0
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "I've been born again in Jesus' name,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 10
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "And in Jesus' name I come to you,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 7
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "To share His love as He told me to.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 3
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 21
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 32
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : ""
    }, {
      "text" : "He said, 'Freely, freely you have received",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 10
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Freely, freely give.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 0
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 15
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Go in my name and because you believe,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 9
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Others will know that I live.'",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 0
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : ""
    }, {
      "text" : "All power is given in Jesus' name,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 4
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "In earth and heaven in Jesus' name,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 3
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "And in Jesus' name, I come to you,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 7
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "To share His power as He told me to.",
      "chords" : [ {
